	     <tr><td valign=top id=fs8 class=mform><span id=notbold>By:</span> <a href=poster.html?user=85776><span id=Sage>Cannis of the Seven Seas</span></a><br><b><span id=Sage>Sage</span></b><br><span id=notbold>690 posts<br><span id=notbold>Score</span>: Excellent [5.00]</td><td valign=top class=mform width=100%><p>I agree with most of your post but 1 never pull with snare the group will hate you when you take long to bring mob to em. Snare should only be used towards the end of the fight so you don't gain agro if your not the main tank. Nothing irritates the tank than a ranger or monk pulling agro from em. <br><br>On point 6 if you get multiple adds snare flamelick and kite till your group is ready to pull one from you.&nbsp;&nbsp;Druid could do same thing but its better for you to do it because if situation deteriorates the druid can port the group out.<br><br><em id=fs8>Edited, Fri Dec 21 11:59:30 2001</em></p>&nbsp;<br>Cannis 65th Ranger<br><a href="http://www.magelo.com/eq_view_profile.html?num=69645" target=_new>http://www.magelo.com/eq_view_profile.html?num=69645</a> <br><br></td></tr>
